<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Требуется Доступ | Дача Зейна' }) %>
    <style>
        body { background: #050608; overflow: hidden; }
        .login-wrapper {
            height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            position: relative; z-index: 2;
        }
        .login-card {
            background: rgba(20, 23, 30, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.3);
            border-radius: 24px; padding: 50px; text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 100px rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px; width: 90%;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        /* Красная полоска сверху */
        .login-card::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px;
            background: #ff5050; box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff5050;
        }
        .icon-lock {
            font-size: 4rem; color: #ff5050; margin-bottom: 20px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.4));
            animation: float 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 800; }
        p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        /* Анимированный фон */
        .bg-grid-red {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    
    <div class="bg-grid-red"></div>

    <div class="login-wrapper">
        <div class="login-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="icon-lock"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
            <h1>Доступ Ограничен</h1>
            <p>Эта зона доступна только авторизованным сотрудникам Улья. <br>Пожалуйста, подтвердите личность.</p>
            
            <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn-primary big" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">
                <i class="fab fa-discord"></i> Войти через Discord
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/vanilla-tilt/1.7.0/vanilla-tilt.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>